# Doxy Project Overview

## Workspaces

| Name | Location |
|------|----------|
| `@doxy/webapp` | `apps/web` |
| `@doxy/design-system` | `packages/design-system` |
| `@doxy/eslint-config` | `packages/eslint-config` |
| `@doxy/typescript-config` | `packages/typescript-config` |

## Key Locations

| Resource | Location |
|----------|----------|
| Scripts | Root `package.json` |
| Design tokens | `packages/design-system/src/tokens/` |
| Component generator | `pnpm generate:component` |

## Quick Commands

```bash
pnpm dev              # Run dev servers
pnpm storybook        # Run Storybook
pnpm test             # Run tests
pnpm lint             # Run all linters
pnpm generate:component  # Scaffold new component
```

For full script list, see root `package.json`.
